    Returns the probability of being seropositive for age-varying force-of-infection including seroreversion

    probability_exact_age_varying.Rd

    Returns the probability of being seropositive for age-varying force-of-infection including seroreversion

    probability_exact_age_varying(age, foi, mu = 0)

    Arguments

    age

    Integer corresponding to the age of the exposed cohort

    foi

    Numeric atomic vector corresponding to the age-varying FoI to simulate from

    mu

    Seroreversion rate

    Value

    probability of being seropositive for age-varying FoI including seroreversion
